  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The insertion of double lumen tube is difficult even more if it is a resident with no
      experience. we think that using videolaryngoscopes for novice ones would facilitate insertion
      of double lumen tube thanks to the visualization on a LCD screen of the laryngeal structure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
